{"tid":1123414,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（護眼）女人真係好恐怖","createTime":"2019-04-24T12:29:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T12:53:48.000Z","uid":35632,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"466375852997fb82f383819e3b4ccc81f5741831","tid":1123414,"uid":35632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T12:29:08.000Z","msg":"成日睇護眼post食花生就多<br />\n估唔到結果有一日落係自己身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兩年半感情 連輸兩次俾唔同台灣仔<br />\n其實第一次都準備好分手<br />\n點知衰心軟一齊番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係好後悔<br />\n講到自己幾為大家嘅將來諗<br />\n口講肯一齊慢慢儲錢 有咩缺點大家攤出黎講一齊改<br />\n去到台灣散心會掛住自己乜乜柒柒<br />\n點知兩次去台灣兩次都玩到失蹤咁 佢平時乖乖女咁款嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nWts幾個鐘先覆 相又唔多張<br />\n都知兇多吉少 都幾撚肯定又俾台仔氹掂<br />\n到共同嘅game line谷有其他台仔腥左幾張成班人去玩嘅相<br />\n其中有張佢同某個台仔著情侶衫嘅相出黎先肯即刻斬欖<br />\n真係忍唔到佢搭返香港班機先講 本來怕影響佢旅行嘅心情<br />\n佢竟然仲夠膽cool煲 <br />\n又講好愛我呀 好多謝我果啲廢話<br />\n差d忍唔住破戒爆粗罵女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知俾台仔中出口爆左幾多鑊啦<br />\n自拍埋床照都敢話冇扑野 淨係攬左陣<br />\n係我咁低能先會信你<br />\n散左一日就即刻轉哂情侶相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係唔敢再信女人 好撚蠱惑<br />\n法國男人專一係冇用嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n半年前個fd俾一齊8年嘅臭雞帽左<br />\n唔通真係專一只係守舊嘅思想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係其實係自己唔夠保鮮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw多謝識左十年嘅中同呢兩日一齊露營散心先冇咁灰<br />\nLove u bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94586f320b74f28db14e3deb365ddb73145e677c","tid":1123414,"uid":35632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T12:35:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09fad4a094ede56d19be79a1525501fe45634701","tid":1123414,"uid":35632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T12:38:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b9dee4369281321b895a85baa6730a3357925e5","tid":1123414,"uid":227968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T12:38:26.000Z","msg":"貼堂啦"},{"pid":"7683ad4a69877819a010454487a8fa8168398543","tid":1123414,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T12:40:20.000Z","msg":"圖呢"},{"pid":"20ffff0e6a0b46e80d97c523c6b0b37746cf40dc","tid":1123414,"uid":31746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T12:45:01.000Z","msg":"法國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8545a2af9367c6262ecebb549800d6e08e504a5d","tid":1123414,"uid":29153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T12:45:32.000Z","msg":"死臭雞"},{"pid":"c9cbcdfe73b2f76115835469437db700733df82b","tid":1123414,"uid":41693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T12:46:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82cfbd0ba00b98b595a82e709fdce17ffdb36c7b","tid":1123414,"uid":168730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T12:46:55.000Z","msg":"轉機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e66de031dc63e5449f8f49a04e01e428682769e4","tid":1123414,"uid":35632,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T12:52:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\"